          "audio": "audio/ViaTestPrep_Unique_1_Part1.mp3",
          "transcript": "<p><b>STAFF:</b> Good morning, Fairview Community Learning Centre, this is Priya speaking. How can I help you today?</p><p><b>CALLER:</b> Hi there. I'd like to sign up for one of your evening classes, please.</p><p><b>STAFF:</b> Of course. Which course are you interested in?</p><p><b>CALLER:</b> The beginner's pottery class on Tuesday evenings.</p><p><b>STAFF:</b> Perfect, I can take your details now. Could I start with your full name?</p><p><b>CALLER:</b> Yes, it's Daniel Whitmore. That's W, H, I, T, M, O, R, E.</p><p><b>STAFF:</b> Thank you. And could I get a contact phone number?</p><p><b>CALLER:</b> Oh-seven-eight-one-six, five-five-two-nine-one-oh.</p><p><b>STAFF:</b> Got it. Now, have you done any pottery before?</p><p><b>CALLER:</b> No, none at all, that's why I'm going for the beginner course.</p><p><b>STAFF:</b> That's exactly what it's designed for. The course runs for 8 weeks, and the fee is 145 pounds, which includes all clay and glazing materials.</p><p><b>CALLER:</b> That sounds reasonable. Do I need to bring anything myself?</p><p><b>STAFF:</b> Just an apron, really. Everything else is provided.</p><p><b>CALLER:</b> Easy enough. And where exactly are the classes held?</p><p><b>STAFF:</b> They're in Room 12, over in the Arts block, not the main building.</p><p><b>CALLER:</b> Room 12, understood. When does the course start?</p><p><b>STAFF:</b> The first session is on the 3rd of September.</p><p><b>CALLER:</b> Perfect. One more thing, is there parking on site?</p><p><b>STAFF:</b> There is, but it's quite limited in the evenings, so we'd recommend using the car park on Bell Street instead, just a 2-minute walk away.</p><p><b>CALLER:</b> Bell Street, got it. Thanks very much for your help.</p><p><b>STAFF:</b> You're very welcome. We'll send a confirmation email once your payment goes through.</p>",
